TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Text: 너 질문 답해 줄 수 있어, 응?

TextEng: Goodbye.
Me want to know about different city areas.
Text: 나 도시 다른 구역들 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What do you know of the plague?
I need infomation about places in Neverwinter.
Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 소문 같은 거 들은 적 있어?

TextEng: You know anything about the bad plague?
Text: 나쁜 역병, 뭐 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Me wants information about places in Neverwinter.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료제를 찾으려는 시도에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
What are the different areas of the city?
Talk about the Beggar's Nest.
Talk about the Docks district.
Talk about the Blacklake district.
Talk about the Peninsula.
Where can I get equipment?
Where me get equipment?
Talk about the City Core.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Shouldn't all help be welcome?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 모든 도움이 환영받아야 하는 거 아냐?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Don't you want the other cure attempts to work?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 다른 치료제를 만드는 시도들이 효과 있길 바라지 않아?

TextEng: Please. I'm sure it will help.
Okay, maybe it help.
If you wish. I doubt it will do anything.
Whatever. It probably do nothing.
No, thank you.
Not for me, no.
I'll not have your useless blessing!
You keep your useless blessing thing!
Text: 그 쓸모없는 축복 같은 건 네가 가져라!

TextEng: I want to ask about the other city districts.
Text: 다른 도시 지구들에 대해 물어보고 싶어.

TextEng: Me ask about other city places.
Is your temple accesible? I may need clerical services.
Text: 성전에 들어갈 수 있어? 성직자의 서비스가 필요할지도 몰라.

TextEng: Your temple open for selling? Me sometimes need cleric stuff.
Text: 너희 사원 문 열려? 가끔 성직자 물건 필요해.

TextEng: How long has the temple been closed?
You been closed for long time?
Can I ask you about Helm's Hold?
Me maybe ask about Helm's Hold?
Has yous collected lots of donations of golds?
Have you collected a lot of charitable donations?
Me just curious. Maybe back to other questions now?
Text: 나 그냥 궁금했어. 다른 질문으로 돌아갈까?

TextEng: I was merely curious. Let's go back to some other questions.
Text: 그냥 궁금했을 뿐이야. 다른 질문으로 돌아가자.

TextEng: You give gold or me shash yous and say yous was stealing it youself!
Text: 너 금 주거나 나 너 때리고 네가 훔치는 거였다고 말할 거야!

TextEng: You give me gold or I'll kill you and claim you were stealing it!
Text: 금 내놔, 안 그러면 죽이고 네가 훔치는 거였다고 할 거야!

TextEng: You right. Me sorry. We forget it happen, okay?
Text: 너 맞아. 나 미안해. 우리 이거 잊자, 알았지?

TextEng: You are right. I'm sorry. Let us forget this.
Text: 당신 말이 맞아요. 미안해요. 이 일은 잊어요.

TextEng: Me serves Aribeth. She believe me, not you. You wants this to get ugly?! Huh?!
Text: 나 아리베스 섬겨. 그녀 나 믿어, 너 안 믿어. 너 이거 더럽게 만들고 싶어?! 응?!

TextEng: I serve Aribeth. She will believe me, not you! Do you want this to get ugly?!
Text: 난 아리베스를 섬겨. 그녀는 널 믿지 않고 날 믿을 거야! 이걸 더럽게 만들고 싶어?!
